data.description: Remarkable upgrades abound! Almost $300,000 in recent, on-trend improvements. This lakefront home sits on an oversized, western-facing lot on a cul-de-sac. It offers 4 bedrooms, 3 bath, 3-car garage with a fabulous saltwater pool & spa and relaxing sun shelf with bubbler, and glow in dark tiles. Enjoy sunset hued evenings from your new screened enclosure with lights and pool deck of leathered marble which features three water jets. The kitchen offers great entertaining space and has brand-new stella quartz countertops and backsplash, LG appliances including new induction stove top and convection oven, EasyClean, Printproof microwave and more. Some upgrades include professionally installed TV built-in and ship lap accent wall with floating butcher block shelves in living room, an air purifier and UV light on AC, storm protection, beautiful acacia wood flooring and crown moulding throughout. Amenities include Resort Pools/Spas, Basketball, Tennis, Playgrounds, Splash Pad, Clubhouse, Fitness Center, Sand Volleyball & Fishing Pier.
